      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Yes that&#39;s why I mentioned the concept of Bootstratpping here, you can refer the article to understand the concept <a href=\"https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/bootstrapping-in-compiler-design/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">geeksforgeeks.org/bootstrapping-in-compiler-design</a>"
